    <h1>Spacing</h1>
    <p class="text-m color-neutral-600">A fluid spacing scale built with Utopia <code>clamp()</code> values that interpolate smoothly between a 320 px minimum and 1240 px maximum viewport — no discrete breakpoints needed.</p>
  </header>

  <section>
    <div class="flow" style="--flow-space: var(--space-s);">
      <h2 class="heading-l">Spacing scale</h2>
      <p>Nine named steps from <code>--space-tiny</code> to <code>--space-huge</code>. Each bar below is sized using the actual token so you can see how the values relate to each other at your current viewport width.</p>

    
